Entity Framework Repository & Unit of Work T4 Template

Author: Dane Morgridge (dane@projectsandbox.com)

This file contains basic information on using this T4 Template and what is included

Folder Structure:

-EFRepositoryBinary : Contains a binary only version that is for extension when using code first. Currently requires EF6
-IRepository.tt : Basic T4 Template with no Dependency Injection framework baked in
-README : this file...



The best place to get information on this project are at the following location:

http://danemorgridge.com


Please feel free to contact me with any questions or additions.

Dane Morgridge
